{"title":"Win N1NO’s Scott Spark RC Custom Cape Epic XC Bike to Support World Bicycle Relief","link":"https://bikerumor.com/win-n1nos-scott-spark-rc-custom-cape-epic-xc-bike-to-support-world-bicycle-relief/","date":1710782072000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-800x533.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" alt=\"Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic custom XC Marathon race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; WBR raffle, riding dirty\" /></p>\n<p>The season-opening Cape Epic kicked off marathon cross-country racing over the weekend, and we’re suckers for the custom XC bikes that the 2-person duos show up on. This year is the 20th anniversary of the iconic South African race, and there are plenty of custom paint jobs marking that milestone. XC legend Nino Schurter is racing a custom-painted <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-scott-spark-gets-bold-new-redesign-as-a-slack-fast-fully-integrated-120mm-xc-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Scott Spark RC</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can’t simply go buy his bike. But Scott-SRAM put an exact replica up for auction to benefit World Bicycle Relief…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>N1NO’s Scott Spark RC Cape Epic Special Edition</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-800x480.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic special edition race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; World Bicycle Relief fundraiser, complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>(Bike photos by Michael Riehle/Scott)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the Absa Cape Epic, Nino Schurter of Scott-SRAM has paired up with friend Sebastian Fini of Lapierre-Mavic Unity – under the combined banner of World Bicycle Relief. “<em>As South Africa is Nino’s favorite place to prepare for the race season, it was clear that the bike had to show the special connection to the country for his attempt to win the Cape Epic for a third time.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>South African custom colors &amp; custom race build </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic special edition race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; World Bicycle Relief fundraiser, cokcpit detaoil\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_top-tube-detail.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For his race bike, Nino’s 120mm Spark RC features “a unique design inspired by the South African national colors and a highly optimized setup for the rugged South African landscape, equipped with the all-new RockShox Flight Attendant XC suspension system”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"582\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-800x582.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic special edition race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; World Bicycle Relief fundraiser, new Flight Attendant XC automatic suspension\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-800x582.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-297x216.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-120x87.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-768x559.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-1536x1117.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_Flight-Attendant-XC-2048x1489.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All kitted out with RockShox SID Ultimate &amp; SIDLuxe Ultimate <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/rockshox-flight-attendant-2024/\" target=\"_blank\">Flight Attendant XC automatic suspension</a> partially hidden inside, a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sram-transmission-eagle-mountain-bike-drivetrain/\" target=\"_blank\">SRAM XX SL Eagle AXS transmission</a>, and conventionally-spoked Syncros Silverton 1.0 carbon wheels on DT hubs.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic special edition race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; World Bicycle Relief fundraiser,SRAM XX SL AXS Transmission\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_SRAM-XX-SL-transmission.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike is set up a bit differently than his usual World Cup race bikes, due to the tougher race environment, and the need to be self-sufficient day-after-day. “<em>No Yanick the Mechanic nearby</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-800x400.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic special edition race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; World Bicycle Relief fundraiser, prepared for repairs\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-800x400.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-297x149.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-120x60.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-768x384.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_prepared-for-trouble-2048x1024.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Scott Spark RC Cape Epic x WBR Auction – Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic custom XC Marathon race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; WBR raffle, N1NO\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_N1NO.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>(Ride photos by Nick Muzik/Scott)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You won’t be able to buy the Scott Spark RC Cape Epic Special Edition, but you might be able to win one. A single Cape Epic x WBR replica is being made just like Nino’s bike. And through a special raffle on VIPrize, interested supporters can buy entries to win this <em><s>one</s> two</em>-off bike. “<em>All proceeds from the raffle will support the nonprofit World Bicycle Relief, which mobilizes people through the Power of Bicycles.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic custom XC Marathon race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; WBR raffle, riding South Africa\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Nick-Muzik_riding-South-Africa.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to the unique bike itself, the winner will get a trip for 2 to the Crans Montana, Switzerland XC World Cup to pick it up. Plus, there are other prizes up for grabs in the WBR fundraiser. Check it out here: <a href=\"https://www.viprize.org/nino\" target=\"_blank\">VIPrize.org/Nino</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Complete Custom Cape Epic Race Bike Spec</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Scott Spark RC x Cape Epic special edition race bike for Nino Schurter &amp; World Bicycle Relief fundraiser, complete angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-Riehle_complete-angled-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024-Scott-Spark-RC-x-Cape-Epic-special-edition-race-bike-for-Nino-Schurter-and-World-Bicycle-Relief-fundraiser_phpoto-by-Michael-R